http://www.savers.org:80/nmp/wr-9-95.html 204.71.237.73 19970108121526 text/html 13225
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 12:15:34 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:00 GMT
Content-length: 13038
