<html>
<head>
<title>TH Kick-Off</title>
</head>

<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">




<CENTER><img src="/townhall/banner-g.gif"><p></CENTER>
<h5><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/welcome.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>


<center>
<b>Town Hall Kick-Off<br>
August 18, 1995</b>
</center>
<hr size="3" width="55%"><p>
Welcome!  This week's EDU-TAINMENT features Town Hall's historical launch on the Internet on June 29, 1995.  The all-day kick-off event featured Senate Majority Leader Bob Dole and House Speaker Newt Gringrich.<p>

I invite you today to re-live our wonderful memories of the event and read the speeches from the conservative leaders who participated.<p>

















<ul>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/kickoff.html.cgi">Complete Opening Remarks</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/dole.html.cgi">Senate Majority Leader Bob Dole</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/gingrich.html.cgi">House Speaker Newt Gingrich</a>
</ul>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/ko-grp.html.cgi">All together now!</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/ko-lect.html.cgi">Lecture Series</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/ko-surf.html.cgi">Surfing the right side</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/ko-rec.html.cgi">Reception</a>
</ul>



<img alt="Picture of Dole and Gingrich" src="newtdole.jpg">

<br>




