<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B019-313</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/townhall/columnists/devine/devi050996.html 204.71.237.73 19970108125847 text/html 7752
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
