<DOCNO>WT16-B40-208</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B024-78</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-11.html 204.71.237.73 19970108131217 text/html 5572
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:12:32 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 13:50:34 GMT
