<DOCNO>WT16-B40-238</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B027-254</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html 204.71.237.73 19970108132236 text/html 6811
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:22:42 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-May-96 15:54:22 GMT
