http://www.savers.org:80/wash_times/pruden.5_5.html 204.71.237.73 19970108133031 text/html 5521
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:30:43 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 28-Apr-96 17:35:22 GMT
Content-length: 5335
