<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/abic/letters/letter-5.html.cgi 204.71.237.73 19970108135322 text/html 4073
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:53:36 GMT
