http://www.savers.org:80/abic/letters/letter-2.html.cgi 204.71.237.73 19970108135431 text/html 7402
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:54:47 GMT
