<a href="/townhall/FRC/whois/whois.html">Who is FRC?</a> | 
<a href="/townhall/FRC/whois/bauer.html">Who is Gary Bauer?</a> | 
<a href="/townhall/FRC/watch.html">Washington Watch</a>
